subSubSection.paragraph:
Amynthas omeimontis (
Chen, 1931
)
from Sichuan, China also has spermathecal pores in 7 / 8 / 9 and numerous small genital papillae. However, it has manicate intestinal caeca, genital papillae absent around spermathecal region and presetal XIX, but about 40 to 50 small papillae closely arranged in rows in presetal XI (
Chen 1931
). Also, it has lower setal number with 38–46 in VI–VIII and 40–44 in XX (
Chen 1931
).
